- Each person maintains THEIR OWN copy of interactions
- Privacy-preserving with consent required

Use Cases:
- Family members sharing memories/experiences
- Research subjects with shared study participation
- Social/group therapy with synchronized tracking
- Collaborative learning between individuals
"""

